         <div type="translation">
            <ab>O. O.I. 19355, recto: These are the names of the twelve apostles: The first is Simon, who is called Peter, and his brother Andrew; Jacob son of Zebedaios and Johannes his brother; Phillip and Bartholomew; Thomas and Matthaios; Jacob son of Alphaios, and Thaddios; Simon the Canaanite and Judas, son of Jacob.</ab>
